getPSDELogicNodes.name: 删除置顶
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: delete from T_IBZ_TOP  where type = 'product' and objectid = ? and account = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 发布数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as RELEASECNT from zt_release t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取相关BUG数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as RELATEDBUGCNT from zt_bug t where t.deleted = '0'  AND t.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 计划数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as PRODUCTPLANCNT from zt_productplan t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取需求数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as DRAFTSTORYCNT from zt_story t where t.deleted = '0'  AND t.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 套件数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as TESTSUITECNT from ZT_TESTSUITE t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and ( t1.`TYPE` = 'public' OR ( t1.`TYPE` = 'private' AND t1.`ADDEDBY` = ? ) ) and t1.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取相关BUG数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as RELATEDBUGCNT from zt_bug t where t.deleted = '0'  AND t.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取测试用例数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as CASECNT from zt_case t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 测试单数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as TESTTASKCNT from ZT_TESTTASK t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.product = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取置顶最大排序值
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select (case when max(t1.`objectorder`) >= 16000000  then max(t1.`objectorder`) + 1 else 16000000 end) as `objectorder` from T_IBZ_TOP t1 where t1.type = 'product' and t1.account= ?
